latestPosts.caption:
40 isn’t just a number — it’s a whole vibe.
A bold becoming. A quiet reckoning. A loud, unapologetic rise.

I’ve lost myself… and found myself in more ways than I can count.
I’ve loved — fiercely, loudly… and in quiet, aching silence.
I’ve broken. I’ve risen.
I’ve become stronger. Softer. Wiser.

Above all — I’ve become grateful.

Grateful for the ones who stayed.
Grateful for the ones who couldn’t.
Because every soul who crossed my path was part of my becoming.

This heart still remembers.And it still chooses love —just with a little more grace.And a lot more truth.

Here’s to 40.
To becoming.
To beginning again. 💫 🙏🏻

#happybirthday #40
